{"word":"ὅπως","slug":"ὅπως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὅπως</el></b> [the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ nt.\">nt.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ rel.\">rel.</a> <el>ὅ, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πῶς\">πῶς</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> introducing details <b>how, that <a href='B:490 24:20'>Lk 24:20</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ conj.\">conj.</a> expressing objective<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> indicating purpose, objective, or end in view <b>(in order) that <a href='B:470 2:8'>Mt 2:8</a>; <a href='B:470 5:45'>5:45</a>; <a href='B:480 3:6'>Mk 3:6</a>; <a href='B:490 2:35'>Lk 2:35</a>; <a href='B:500 11:57'>J 11:57</a>; <a href='B:510 3:20'>Ac 3:20</a>; <a href='B:510 9:17'>9:17</a>; <a href='B:520 3:4'>Ro 3:4</a>; <a href='B:530 1:29'>1 Cor 1:29</a>; <a href='B:540 8:14'>2 Cor 8:14</a>; <a href='B:550 1:4'>Gal 1:4</a>; <a href='B:600 1:12'>2 Th 1:12</a>; <a href='B:650 2:9'>Hb 2:9</a>; <a href='B:670 2:9'>1 Pt 2:9</a>;</b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to divine intention expressed in linkage of event and sacred scripture in the formulation <el>ὅπ. πληρωϑῇ</el> in fulfillment of <b><a href='B:470 2:23'>Mt 2:23</a>; <a href='B:470 8:17'>8:17</a>; <a href='B:470 12:17'>12:17</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> (= <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἵνα\">ἵνα</a></el>); <b><a href='B:470 13:35'>13:35</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> introducing petition or request <b><a href='B:470 8:34'>Mt 8:34</a>; <a href='B:470 9:38'>9:38</a>; <a href='B:490 7:3'>Lk 7:3</a>; <a href='B:490 11:37'>11:37</a>; <a href='B:510 23:20'>Ac 23:20</a>; <a href='B:510 25:3'>25:3</a>; <a href='B:660 5:16'>Js 5:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> suggesting procedure <b>as to how <a href='B:470 12:14'>Mt 12:14</a>; <a href='B:470 22:15'>22:15</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:640 1:1'>Phlm 6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀπώρα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὅραμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}